{"version":3,"term":{"cols":80,"rows":24},"timestamp":1776849418,"command":"bash /Users/jang-ujin/study/forgen/docs/demo/mech-b-demo.sh","env":{"SHELL":"/bin/zsh"}}
[0.020, "o", "\r\n\u001b[36m═══ forgen v0.4.0 — The Trust Layer in action ═══\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[1.014, "o", "\u001b[2m# This is an L1 rule forgen ships as dogfood:\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.750, "o", "{\r\n    \"rule_id\": \"L1-e2e-before-done\",\r\n    \"category\": \"quality\",\r\n    \"scope\": \"me\",\r\n    \"trigger\": \"completion-before-e2e\",\r\n    \"policy\": \"forgen \\ud504\\ub85c\\uc81d\\ud2b8\\uc5d0\\uc11c \\ubcc0\\uacbd \\ud6c4 vitest \\ub9cc\\uc73c\\ub85c \\uc644\\ub8cc \\uc120\\uc5b8 \\uae08\\uc9c0. \\ubc18\\ub4dc\\uc2dc Docker e2e (tests/e2e/docker/run-test.sh \\ub610\\ub294 equivalent) \\ud1b5\\uacfc \\uc99d\\uac70\\uac00 ~/.forgen/state/e2e-result.json \\uc5d0 \\ucd5c\\uadfc 1\\uc2dc\\uac04 \\ub0b4 \\uc0dd\\uc131\\ub418\\uc5b4\\uc57c \\uc644\\ub8cc.\",\r\n    \"strength\": \"hard\",\r\n    \"source\": \"explicit_correction\",\r\n    \"status\": \"active\",\r\n    \"evidence_refs\": [],\r\n    \"render_key\": \"quality_safety.l1-e2e-before-done\",\r\n    \"created_at\": \"2026-04-22T00:00:00.000Z\",\r\n    \"updated_at\": \"2026-04-22T00:00:00.000Z\",\r\n    \"enforce_via\": [\r\n"]
[2.516, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[2m# It says: 'no \"done\" claim without fresh Docker e2e evidence'.\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[1.513, "o", "\u001b[36mTurn 1 — Claude just said \"구현 완료했습니다.\" \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m# forgen's Stop hook reads Claude's last message:\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.512, "o", "\u001b[2m$ echo '<Stop hook input>' | node dist/hooks/stop-guard.js\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.337, "o", "{\r\n    \"continue\": true,\r\n    \"decision\": \"block\",\r\n    \"reason\": \"[forgen:stop-guard/L1-e2e-b] L1-e2e-before-done: \\uc644\\ub8cc \\uc120\\uc5b8 \\uc804 Docker e2e \\uc99d\\uac70 (~/.forgen/state/e2e-result.json, 1\\uc2dc\\uac04 \\uc774\\ub0b4) \\ud544\\uc694. \\uc9c0\\uae08 \\uc2e4\\ud589 \\ud6c4 \\uc7ac\\uc751\\ub2f5\\ud558\\ub77c.\\n\\n(Override this turn: set FORGEN_USER_CONFIRMED=1 (audited). Disable rule permanently: `forgen suppress-rule L1-e2e-before-done`. See recent blocks: `forgen last-block`.)\",\r\n    \"systemMessage\": \"rule:L1-e2e-before-done\"\r\n}\r\n"]
[3.012, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[2m# decision=block. Claude sees this 'reason' as input on the next turn.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[2m# Same session, same prompt budget — zero extra API calls.\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[2.011, "o", "\u001b[36mTurn 2 — Claude (in real Claude Code) would retract and run e2e:\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.507, "o", "\u001b[2m$ bash tests/e2e/docker/run-test.sh  # 63 checks, real Docker suite\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.029, "o", "\u001b[32m  Results: 63 passed, 0 failed, 6 warnings\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32m  ✅ ALL CHECKS PASSED\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[2.005, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[36mTurn 3 — Claude re-submits \"구현 완료했습니다.\":\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.094, "o", "{\"continue\":true}\r\n"]
[2.009, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[2m# Evidence is fresh → rule passes → Claude proceeds. User trust preserved.\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[2.006, "o", "\u001b[36mAudit trail: forgen last-block\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.907, "o", "    L1-e2e-before-done       1\r\n\r\n  Recent (time — rule_id — kind@source — preview):\r\n    2026-04-22T09:17:07  L1-e2e-before-done        block     @stop-guard      구현 완료했습니다.\r\n\r\n  Resolve:\r\n    Disable a rule:   forgen suppress-rule <rule_id>\r\n    Re-enable:        forgen activate-rule <rule_id>\r\n    Temp bypass turn: set FORGEN_USER_CONFIRMED=1 (audited)\r\n\r\n"]
[3.015, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[2m# That's it. Rule, block, evidence, unblock, audit — at $0 extra API.\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[0.009, "x", "0"]
